<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/adrian-hannell> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Adrian Hannell was appointed Interim Director of Finance and Digital at the Legal Aid Agency in September 2017. He joined the Legal Aid Agency in April 2016 as Deputy Director of Finance. Before that, Adrian worked as finance director for a number of businesses within Capita PLC, and also held a variety of finance roles at Alliance Boots. Adrian began his career at Ernst & Young where he qualified as a chartered accountant."@en .
